---
title: Shawarma-Rama Green Pea & Feta Patties with Yellow Rice, Roasted Veggies & Garlic Lemon Sauce
description: It’s hard NOT to love a deliciously-crisp, superb patty. Here, our chefs mixed mashed green peas, briny feta, and onion in tempura batter seasoned with Shawarma Spices. The result—flavor-packed patties that fry up crispy outside, tender inside and are irresistible with a drizzle of a creamy garlic-lemon sauce. Serve with fluffy, fragrant turmeric rice and roasted zucchini, red onion, and tomatoes, and fall in love all over again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/green-pea-feta-patties-58e22dd8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/shawarma-rama-green-pea-feta-patties-633c68b1a6f0337ca6014f62-ceee5809.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shawarma-rama-green-pea-and-feta-patties-633c68b1a6f0337ca6014f62
cuisine: Mediterranean
servings: 2
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 810 kcal
  fat: 38 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
